Based on the analysis presented here, we believe that regimebased asset allocation has the potential to deliver significant benefits when compared to traditional investment policies, which are most commonly static and benchmark based. Contingent on good economic foresight, implementation of a regime-based approach can potentially add to cumulative performance over time, translating to an improved distribution of overall portfolio returns.},
