We discuss an optimal asset allocation problem in a regime-switching model. We expand investment opportunity sets in a stochastic interest rate environment. The impacts of regime switches on optimal portfolio strategies are examined. The effects of stochastic interest rates on optimal portfolios are investigated. Both regime switches and the market price of interest rate risk are significant.},
